            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                φυλὴ Α<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> δι’ ἐπιμελητοῦ</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Πλαυτ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>ανοῦ Ἀλε<supplied reason="lost">ξάνδρου</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Τ(ίτον) Φλάο<supplied reason="lost">υ</supplied>ιον Ἀμύντο<supplied reason="lost">υ υἱὸν</supplied> <lb n="4"/>Παράμονον τὸν ἀρ<supplied reason="lost">χιε</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>ρέα τῶν Σεβαστῶν καὶ ἀ<supplied reason="lost">γω</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/>νοθ<supplied reason="lost">έ</supplied>την τοῦ κοινοῦ <supplied reason="lost">Μα</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"/>κεδ<supplied reason="lost">όν</supplied>ων υἱὸν πόλεως δ<supplied reason="lost">ὶς</supplied> <lb n="8"/>γ<supplied reason="lost">υμν</supplied>ασίαρχον δόντα <supplied reason="lost">μο</supplied><lb break="no" n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">νομά</supplied>χια καὶ θηριομ<supplied reason="lost">άχια</supplied> <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">ἐν ταῖς</supplied> γυμνασ<supplied reason="lost">ιαρχίαις</supplied> <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">ἑαυτὸν</supplied> ἀπ<supplied reason="lost">ροφασίστως</supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift besteht aus zwei sich anschließenden Fragmenten. Die Maße des kleineren Fragments sind: Höhe: -40; Breite: -24; Tiefe: 5. (B): Die Ergänzung in Z. 12 und die Alternativlesung in Z. 9 sind im Text nicht berücksichtigt.</p>
            </div>
